rComments: He's super funny and cares about his students. He takes time to get to know you when you're in smaller groups. Final grade depends on the completion of homework so get to class and make sure you get it done.
He gives you that high school vibe, the course is a joke, it's literally a le/la situation. He's funny.
He's soooo funny and cute !! take him, not only the course is easy but just by the way he's teaching it you can tell he has experience in this field.

Funniest prof hands down !! He's soo down to earth & always brings up anecdotes. This course is beyond easy I'm talking middle school easy but you have to attend class, there's more than 3 tests, attendance is mandatory since you are graded for it. There's also easy homeworks every other class that he sometimes checks and gives you points for.
He is the funniest prof. High quality instructor. the class was easy too.

Awesome prof. Easy class. Fun to attend. He is so cute and funny! He cares of all students and want you to succeed. Do the little homework and dont be shy to talk to him. He loves to talk to students. Such a caring prof! I recommend!!!
C'est un cours très facile qui requiert peu d'effort. En plus, le prof est tellement drôle!!
Alot of small funny stories Care alot for students Will make anything to make class easier 10/10 would take FRA1705 again
He's a great teacher.
Really funny, always there for his students!
He is an amazing prof and you really do learn a lot in this class!! It's a very small class so he is really accessible if you need help!! I would take this class again if I had the choice!
Does anyone have his email address ?
Un bac en DLS c'est un bac en Monsieur Allain et c'est tant mieux. C'est le meilleur prof de l'université d'Ottawa!

He is the most amazing prof!! So funny and a bundle of joy. He is always making class super fun and tells funny jokes. Always has creative ideas for activities. (example..the chip ahoy activity YUMMY!) P.S He is so cute and he looks like a celebrity..I forgot which one) Anywase TAKE HIS CLASS and please teach more:)

A bloody good prof! He is fair and I do not agree that he gives Anglophones a rough time. If anything, he is a generous grader. Has the most hilarious expressions and is passionate about teaching. He is the Johnny Cash of the Faculty, always in black. A good chap.
Super teacher.  Enthusiastic and passionate about his subject matter.  I would take more classes if he taught them.  Merci!
A fun prof who really teaches!
great
Great guy! Funny stories, explains things clearly & numerous times if needed. Lets us have cheat sheets for tests!
Really fun and exciting. You are always wondering what he will come up with next. He has great teaching stories but is hard on Anglophone students. He is keen on perfection.
Very nice prof
Best Teacher ever!!  Two thumbs up!!!  If you can, take his class!
Loves himself too muc. Wants to be popular not teach!
a great prof, he really encourages you to want to teach, repeats his stories sometimes but he makes up for it, no final!
He's nice and fun in class but he tends to be too busy to help outside the class. I think the school gives him too much work for him to be 100% of a good teacher. He's kind of repetitive.

Excellent prof, TRES dynamique et amical.  Veut vraiment donner le meilleur cours possible et reussit a transmettre des connaissances de base pratiques et des concepts plus avances sans nous ennuyer ou nous perdre. L'accent acadien, j'adore!
